<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up 1.91 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, October 3 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1,535.56 points on Saturday, up
1.91 points compared to the figure on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,679,845 shares worth 4.43 billion rials (805,000
U.S. dollars) changed hands in 808 turns for 376 applicants. The
shares of 42 companies made gains while those of six others
declined. 
</P>
