<HEADLINE> New Zealand Surprises Australia in Oceania Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, October 4 (Xinhua) -- Underdog New Zealand booked a
berth for next year's Confederations'Cup after a 1-0 surprising
victory over Australia on Sunday in the Oceania Nations Cup final
in Brisbane, Australia.
