border areas Hassan Barati termed Taliban's claim as "mere lie,"
the Iranian official news agency IRNA reported.
</P>
<P>
A Taliban spokesman said on Friday that several Iranian jet
fighters intruded into the Afghan airspace that day and broke
sound barrier.
</P>
